Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:16.24,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Komachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.22,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:20.70,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:24.04,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Want some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:26.89,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:29.20,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:40.37,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:45.52,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Komachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.37,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.38,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.14,0:01:10.75,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.36,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:15.83,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.83,0:01:17.47,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have said it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:19.11,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't just the {\i1}way{\i0} you said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:21.59,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Your attitude was lousy, too. \NAnd your personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:22.63,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Also, your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:24.02,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:27.48,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's your fault because \Nof something you did, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.05,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:30.78,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,And you haven't apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:32.52,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Very true...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:35.24,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,But you're my brother, \Nand that's who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:36.74,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your sister, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.20,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:39.96,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.59,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:46.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't sweat it. I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:47.68,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your brother, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:50.04,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, you're so full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.33,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:54.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,This could take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:56.44,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:04.56,Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,1)}My Teen\NRomantic\NComedy\N{\c&H8D39E0&}SNAFU\N{\c&HDCA02E&}TOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:30.48,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's so like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:34.70,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, the only reason I \Nunderstand that is because I'm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:37.73,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I understand because I've \Nlived with you all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.93,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I can just say, "He's so stupid," \Nand laugh it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.42,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I can think, "He really is hopeless."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.27,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,And then... I feel a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.29,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,But other people aren't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.25,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,They don't understand at all, \Nand I'm sure it really hurts them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.02,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're nice to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:58.38,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,but you can only do that because \NI'm your sister, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:01.04,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,If I weren't your sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.97,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,you'd probably never even \Ncome anywhere near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:06.46,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that whole mechanism aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.53,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're my sister, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd give myself a lot \Nof points for that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.40,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:21.44,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know I'd never go near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.57,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't even take notice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:27.63,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you say that, but I have \Nmy good qualities, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.22,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. Come on, don't be such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:34.50,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:37.38,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,After fifteen years together,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.19,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,you just think that's how it \Nought to be, and grow fond of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.84,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'd give myself a lot \Nof points for that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.39,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, after fifteen years together, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.62,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,It could be another fifteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:51.09,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, even longer than that from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.47,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't split hairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.60,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,How many years do you think I've \Nlistened to you splitting hairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:58.02,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to now, \Nand you're always going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:04:59.25,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:01.53,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.36,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.28,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be around a while longer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:09.64,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I like Yukino-san and Yui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.79,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't want that club to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:15.80,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,So, for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:19.42,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,For my friends... \NIs there anything you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.42,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for my sister, what choice do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.06,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:28.61,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a selfish girl, after all. \NWhat're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:29.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.14,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.46,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:43.92,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's one answer, given to me by Komachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.96,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, I've been \Ntrying to find a reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:51.14,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,A reason for me to protect that \Nplace, and our time there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.15,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,To keep both Yukinoshita Yukino
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:56.00,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and Yuigahama Yui from becoming \Nstudent council president...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.94,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What can Hikigaya Hachiman do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.84,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.57,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,absolutely nothing, and it's killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:10.17,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about wearing our \Nown clothes to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.08,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:14.10,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,And it'd be nice to get rid of the \Npersonal belongings searches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.93,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I hate those.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:18.98,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes have doujinshi I \Nborrowed from my friends in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.10,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's just you, Ebina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:22.06,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll write it down, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.36,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to write that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.77,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I want to eat lunch up on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:28.11,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:37.91,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,You look pitiful, Hikigaya Hachiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.92,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:43.51,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful is my default state.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.85,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.36,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,A foolish question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.61,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,I spend my lunch breaks in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:52.66,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,and I saw you, so I thought \NI'd come pester you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.73,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Hachiman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:57.43,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. It's dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.86,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:02.22,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. It's not worth talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.65,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:08.31,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have you \Nlistened to my idle chatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:11.29,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gladly listen to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:16.70,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, look at me, reaching out \Nto the weak. I'm so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.46,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That last line was cool, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:21.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So who'd you steal it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:21.92,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.42,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:27.07,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. Don't say stuff that's actually cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.49,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Zaimokuza, I need a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:32.43,saizeriya_07:30,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Saizeriya
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.43,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So the question is what exactly I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.19,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:40.24,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.91,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna work hard for my sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:45.15,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I figure I've gotta work hard, too. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:48.23,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! I got some people to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.32,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.78,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,So this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:55.36,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Operation: Stop Yukino-san and \NYui-san from Leaving the Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:56.59,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.37,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Look, not that I care,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:03.75,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,but if Yukinoshita and Yuigahama don't \Ndo it, who's gonna be president?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:04.58,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.25,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:10.69,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Why can't we let \Nthem be elected, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:15.14,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. The very idea of battling \Nthem is wrong in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.43,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:22.06,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, I just want Yukino-san and \NYui-san to stay in the Service Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:25.15,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I couldn't care \Nless about any election.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.44,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.90,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But then Isshiki would...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:32.33,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Isshiki-san person important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.61,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.03,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:37.86,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, a request is a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:40.10,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more important, your work or me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.56,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.04,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.62,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Process of elimination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:47.36,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really be happy about that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.63,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.58,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.43,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.83,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to assign top priority
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:09:01.14,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,to Komachi's request of keeping \NYukinoshita and Yuigahama in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.85,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But it's going to be tough to \Nback any other candidates,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.07,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,so the only card I have left to play is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.57,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess all I can do is \Nnegotiate with Isshiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.24,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.49,Ore_Main,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Can you talk to a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:19.07,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If Isshiki Iroha is putting \Non that character as an act,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:21.89,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,that's actually ideal for negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:26.46,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,In short, Isshiki wants to protect \Nher own self-branded image.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:31.89,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why she didn't want a \Nhigh-risk, low-return vote of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.38,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:36.25,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been taking the wrong \Napproach from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:38.39,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Kawasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:42.16,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the names of some \Npeople you think might make a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.56,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,good student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.31,name_list_09:45,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita\NYuigahama\NHayama\NEbina\NMiura\NSagami\NTobe
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.92,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,And... you, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.37,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Ha, very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:55.62,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not gonna find \Nthirty people to back me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:58.03,Ore_Main,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. I just thought I'd say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.37,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:02.69,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you talk to \NYukino-san and Yui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:03.87,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:08.00,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but it won't do any \Ngood if it's not convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.60,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to prepare first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.84,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,You seem so logical, but you always \Nblow things off along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.88,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.26,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:20.01,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been given a reason, established the \Nproblem, and obtained the means.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:23.64,name_list_09:45,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita\NYuigahama\NHayama\NEbina\NMiura\NSagami\NTobe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.84,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Now I just have to carry it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.60,hayamaWB_10:24,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-kun Support Account
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.60,hayamaBW_10:24,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-kun Support Account\NHayama Hayato-kun for President!\NNot much time left until the\Nstudent council election!\NHayama Hayato for President
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:34.46,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think we should have LCD \Ngraphics tablets in the art room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.23,yukinoshitaWP_10:33,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita Yukino Support Account
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.23,hayamaBW_10:24,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita Yukino Support Account\NNot much time left until the student\Ncouncil election! Yukinoshita Yukino\Nfor President Hayama-kun Support\NAccount  This is our candidate! Seeking\Nbackers. RT if you'll let us list you as a backer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.23,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,LCD?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:47.56,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,A third of the entire student body, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:51.67,Ore_Italics,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,It is I.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:54.81,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We've got enough. \NLet's move to the next phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.84,hayamaBW_10:24,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-kun Support Account\NHayama Hayato-kun for President! / This\Naccount is seeking backers for Hayama-kun.\NPlease follow & RT to show your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.52,Ore_Italics,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say I wholly commend this method.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:10:59.84,Ore_Italics,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:00.97,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Zaimokuza...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.85,Ore_Italics,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.45,Ore_Italics,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:06.53,Ore_Italics,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried that I'll be held \Nresponsible for executing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:10.11,Ore_Italics,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,that you'll drop me like a lizard drops \Nits tail to save itself. Nothing more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:13.47,Ore_Italics,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll warn you that I am prepared to \Nexpose you, should that be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:16.03,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a scumbag, \Nit's almost refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.70,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.24,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if anyone tries to find us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:21.11,Edit_Profile_11:18,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Edit Profile
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.71,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,the person behind this \Naccount doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.62,hayasupport_11:21,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-kun Support Account
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:23.62,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No one will take any damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.76,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware, Zaimokuza?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:30.47,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So long as a problem doesn't cause \Nproblems, it can't be called a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.88,Class_1C_11:30,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Class 1-C
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:33.50,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Could you get Isshiki-san for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:39.00,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:44.01,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, it's such a pain to copy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:48.49,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, was that girl you were out with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.70,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the other day Hayama-senpai's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:51.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:55.18,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, come on. You can tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.60,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,After we finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:01.77,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that's all it was, it doesn't \Nseem like there'll be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.03,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.70,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, do you l—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.53,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:10.79,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.50,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Are you hitting on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.75,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I can't. There's someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:19.43,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I only wanted to know what you \Nthink of him, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:22.13,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:25.40,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,If I thought things were going \Nwell, I'd try to make a gr—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:28.24,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,To hold his hand, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.93,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,She just started to say \N"make a grab," didn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:34.77,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Senpai! Is there any \Npoint in doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.97,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there isn't {\i1}not{\i0} one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:39.43,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of a vague answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:41.80,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you try to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.80,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,you can't beat Yukinoshita and Yuigahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense, no, there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:53.58,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like I want to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:57.54,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'd actually happen \Nto win, it'd be kinda scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.75,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you can top them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.55,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:08.02,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And even the people who initially \Nbacked you won't vote for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:12.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,They must be laughing their heads off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:16.14,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll laugh even harder \Nwhen they see you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.19,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That probably pisses you off, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:23.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If someone does something to \Nyou, you should get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.80,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, if I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:28.67,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:34.00,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think this thing \NI've been having you write is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.95,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Lists of backers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:37.50,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:40.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Isshiki Iroha's list of backers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:41.56,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:43.80,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:48.24,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I already have my backers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:51.20,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The rule is that you need at least thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.19,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You can get as many as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:57.17,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's a support account \Nfor you on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.44,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,A third of the student body follows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.48,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,With this many supporters, you can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:04.94,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I can't pull it off just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:08.64,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,And even if I did win, I don't \Nthink I could handle the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.78,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.53,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,And I have my club, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:15.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it certainly would \Nbe tough to juggle both.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.85,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something great to gain from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:18.29,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.59,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.40,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, experience and stuff, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.30,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,And it'd look good on my record...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.72,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Senpai, you sound like a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.68,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong. Listen. What you'd gain is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:36.23,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm student council president as a \Nfirst-year, but I still attend my own club!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:36.93,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.18,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Ew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.15,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,A first-year would be forgiven for failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.57,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And when you don't want to \Ndo student council work,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.29,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,you could use your club as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.01,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The other way around would work, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:51.82,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,B-But it would be hard work, \Nwouldn't it? Or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If it gets to that point, \Nyou can talk to Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.84,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well have him help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:15:01.19,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If you catch him after your club, \Nyou'd get the perk of him walking you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:08.53,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, are you actually really smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:09.52,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:15.22,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I have this much support, \NI guess there's not much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:19.10,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,And that proposal is \Nattractive in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:23.60,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't want people in my class \Nlaughing at me behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.24,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you twist my arm, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.67,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You guys won't change your minds?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.27,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:39.96,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I won't, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:42.33,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.46,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I will run. And I don't intend to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:46.58,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:49.82,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Because without you, we'll have no club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:51.84,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.61,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It won't come to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:54.51,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:57.26,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There really is no need for you to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:00.39,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Not just for Yuigahama, \Nbut for you either, Yukinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.48,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.84,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we rejected your idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.73,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You did. I don't mean that idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:08.93,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I gave up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:13.99,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.01,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been some sympathizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.74,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who, or where they came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:18.98,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:20.58,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:23.75,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. At least a third of \Nthe entire student body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:25.88,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Those numbers are the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:30.71,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's not possible for Isshiki \NIroha to gather that much support.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:34.22,Ore_Flashback_Italics,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Just don't end up making me take the \Nblame for this! Seriously, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:34.22,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That means there's just one big lie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.91,Ore_Flashback,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.35,Edit_Profile_11:18 - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Edit Profile
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:41.64,Ore_Flashback_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing but a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.80,hayasupport_11:21,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-kun Support Account
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.41,Ore_Flashback_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,A starting point for me \Nto convince the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:47.71,Ore_Flashback_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So I just have to get through today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:45.43,hayasupport_11:21,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki Iroha Support Account
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.68,miura_16:45,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Miura Yumiko Support Account
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:48.69,Ishhiki_16:47,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki Iroha Support Account
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:49.73,Ore_Flashback_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll delete the account altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.68,Totsuka_16:48,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuka Saika Support Account
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.36,Ore_Flashback_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It will all disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.82,Isshiki_16:50,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki Iroha Support Account
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:57.35,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,This clears all the conditions we were \Nbound by for making Isshiki president.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:58.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:01.66,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for either of you to \Nbe student council president now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:07.84,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,"Support account"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:22.84,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.31,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's solved, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:33.86,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:38.38,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's no problem, nor any \Nreason for me to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.83,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:41.92,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.62,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You thought you understood, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.40,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go report to the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:54.30,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.30,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.90,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.07,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:19.16,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you worked hard on \Na lot of stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:22.15,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Like your pledge, and your campaign speech...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:24.86,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.98,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You did a lot, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:30.33,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you let your hair grow \Nout and get all scruffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:31.65,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:32.87,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.30,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:41.07,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:41.87,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:52.22,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You protected the place
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.23,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,that's most important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:00.28,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the truth is, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:03.33,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That I probably couldn't beat Yukinon,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.25,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,and that if I did win and became president,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:08.58,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to come to this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:12.29,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,So it's all thanks to you, Hikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.70,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.40,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:30.27,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.65,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Where's this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.49,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:36.92,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out. I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:40.45,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... You didn't do \Nanything that we could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:42.75,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But if we could have,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:44.95,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we would've seen you \Ndoing something that wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:50.45,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think your methods can be \Nchanged, even if you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.04,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Guilt doesn't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.48,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:20:00.30,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,but I still can't help thinking \Nthis was for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:02.82,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,So it must be even more so for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:06.81,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,We can all go back to normal now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.37,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:13.45,Ore_Flashback,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You thought you understood, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:17.95,Ore_Flashback,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This club isn't that demanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:21.00,Ore_Flashback,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}and I understand the work that comes \Nwith being on the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:22.93,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If they're not given a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:23.65,Ore_Flashback,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}My doing this was the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.40,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,if they're unable to find a reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:25.68,Ore_Flashback,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Even against Isshiki-san, I can win easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:28.45,Ore_Flashback,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And I don't mind doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.45,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,some people can't bring themselves to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:32.21,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I got something wrong somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.96,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Only that bit of doubt stayed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.46,Winners_20:34,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council President\NIsshiki Iroha  Winner\NVice President\NHonmoku Makito  Winner\NSecretary\NFujisawa Sawako  Winner\NTreasurer\NInamura Jun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:37.46,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're starting work today already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:39.21,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:42.97,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt anything will come \Nof it at first, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:46.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's going to be \Nstarting here next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.22,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So make this a good school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.60,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Are you hitting on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:56.42,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, you're trying too hard and \Nit's creeping me out and I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:59.07,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the reason you gave \Nfor rejecting me last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:01.09,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.53,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hikigaya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.50,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:10.23,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I didn't realize \Nhow much stuff I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.72,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,It sort of looks like a different room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.71,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I had my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:23.42,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:27.18,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be great if \NYukinoshita-san became president.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.68,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,And Yuigahama-san would be vice president,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:31.36,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,and you'd handle general affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:33.43,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who doesn't \Nget an official position?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:34.77,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:38.97,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,After graduation, I'd drop in to visit \Nthe student council now and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:44.53,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,and we'd talk about how much fun the \Ncultural and athletic festivals were.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:48.51,Ore_Main,Meguri,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of always wanted to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:54.84,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Rhetorically speaking... \NStrictly rhetorically...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:22:00.45,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If it were possible to return to the \Nprevious save point, like in a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:03.26,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and make a different choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.17,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,would life change?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:09.17,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,The Scent of Tea\NDoesn't Fill That Room Anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:08.47,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is "no."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:24:08.46,Next_Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,#06 Without Incident, The Congress Dances, But Does Not Progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:40.95,Ore_Main_Top,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Irohas!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.95,0:23:43.23,Ore_Main_Top,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there's nothing \Nelse to carry, Irohas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:46.22,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Tobe-senpai, the fridge doesn't \Ngo there. It goes in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:47.99,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,And the heater goes beside the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:50.09,Ore_Main_Top,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd said that sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:53.24,Ore_Main_Top,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Irohas, I've got a Christmas \Nseason part-time job to get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.27,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have anything to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.27,0:23:57.91,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get the student council \Nroom rearrangement out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:23:58.95,Ore_Main_Top,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.95,0:24:00.51,Ore_Main_Top,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,I've got work, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:02.83,Ore_Main_Top,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Hayato-kun, hurry up and get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:04.33,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:06.93,Ore_Main_Top,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Tobe-senpai, that's enough. You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.93,0:24:07.97,Ore_Main_Top,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.97,0:24:09.97,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
